    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "A Maritime Christmas with Jud Gunning "
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p> A Maritime Christmas with Jud Gunning returns for its second year, celebrating the warmth, tradition, and musical spirit of the season through an authentic East Coast lens. Featuring rising Nova Scotia performer Jud Gunning, the show blends heartfelt storytelling with classic guitar-driven arrangements inspired by the greats of country, folk, and roots music.\nBuilding on a successful debut, this year's production continues to showcase Jud's growing artistry and deep connection to Maritime musical heritage, delivering an intimate and festive evening that highlights both timeless Christmas favourites and the rich sounds of Atlantic Canada. </p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
