      {
        "@value": "<p>Internationally touring comedian Jeff Leeson returns to Shelburne with a brand new show for a night of Live stand up comedy you will NEVER forget! With over 25 years experience touring North America and over 100 Million views online, find out why this is definitely one show you absolutely Do Not want to miss!</p>\n\n<style>\n    .titleTax {\n       display: none !important;\n   }\n</style>\n\n"
