    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "SLC TOUR - MacDougall, MacIsaac, MacLellan"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>This August, three incredible female Singer/Songwriters come together for the first time on the Osprey stage. With dozens of music industry awards and nominations between them, these women will conjure an evening of songs and stories that will leave you spellbound and aching for more. Sarah MacDougall is known for her poetic songs and passionate performances. Lisa MacIsaac is one half of the acclaimed Madison Violet duo. Catherine MacLellan, daughter of music legend, Gene, has been captivating audiences over two decades and seven albums of folk/roots rock. Together, they promise a show you won't forget.</p>\n\n<style>\n    .titleTax {\n       display: none !important;\n   }\n</style>\n\n"
      }
    ],
