      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "The Rolling Stones Experience - Featuring The Blushing Brides"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Since 1979, the Blushing Brides have been cranking out their versions of the hits from Satisfaction and Midnight Rambler to Gimme Shelter. A cover band that grabbed the attention of the Rolling Stones guitarist Keith Richards, who said it was a 'brilliant rendition.' </p> \n\n<p>With thousands of performances in multiple countries under their belts, it becomes abundantly clear early in their exceptional and energetic show performance, that they are something exceedingly special and excessively unique.</p> \n\n<p>A musical group that has the uncanny ability to harness the stage presence, energy level and excitement that only the Rolling Stones could previously deliver. The Blushing Brides distinctive signature sound and delivery has distinguished themselves as a group whose concert events deliver an unparalleled energy, intense passion & spontaneity.</p> \n\n<p>The Blushing Brides show is infectious, and engulfs the audience in Rolling Stones mojo to the point that audience participation in and of itself, becomes an integral part of this rock'n'roll extravaganza.</p> \n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/qC04q0ol7Xg?si=GZ2UbNMKWNRccQ11' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
