    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Woody Point Summer Concert Series - Jodee & Nicole - What odds?! tour"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>It's a special feeling to sit in the Woody Point Heritage Theatre on a warm summer night. The audience gathers, the ocean breeze winds its way through the windows, and the music drifts out over Bonne Bay.</p>\n\n<p>We have some exciting performances planned for our Summer Concert Series this year, including Tim Baker and Silver Wolf Band. We look forward to welcoming you through the doors of the Woody Point Heritage Theatre.</p>\n\n<p>Find more information: <a href='http://www.writersatwoodypoint.com/' target='_blank'>www.writersatwoodypoint.com</a></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n.location-event-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>\n"
